---
// Componente About para la sección "About me"
---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-4 md:gap-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <span class="section-name icon-right animate-in-up">
          <span class="section-name-caption">About me</span>
          <i class="ph ph-arrow-down-right"></i>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8 flex flex-col gap-12 md:gap-24">
        <h2 class="reveal-type animate-in-up">My <span>Developer's Path</span></h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
          <!-- 01 - The Beginning -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-start animate-in-up">
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3 flex flex-col">
              <h3 class="heading-3 mb-2">
                01. <small class="block text-base font-normal opacity-75" style="font-size:50%"
                  >The Beginning</small
                >
              </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9">
              <p>
                I'm not the typical developer. A long time ago, my journey began — over 20 years ago
                — as a young padawan discovering the early powers of <span class="font-bold"
                  >visuals</span
                >, <span class="italic">motion</span>, and <span class="font-bold italic"
                  >detail</span
                >. That's where the first skills took shape: <span class="font-bold"
                  >pixel-perfect layouts</span
                >, <span class="italic">smooth interactions</span>, and <span class="font-bold"
                  >interfaces that felt alive</span
                >.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 02 - The Evolution -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-start animate-in-up">
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3 flex flex-col">
              <h3 class="heading-3 mb-2">
                02. <small class="block text-base font-normal opacity-75" style="font-size:50%"
                  >The Evolution</small
                >
              </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9">
              <p>
                But style alone wasn't enough. The real power came when I embraced the other side of
                the stack — <span class="font-bold">solving complex challenges</span>, <span
                  class="italic">building integrations</span
                >, and <span class="font-bold">connecting systems</span>. Some might call it <span
                  class="italic">the dark side of development</span
                >. I call it <span class="font-bold">balance</span>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 03 - The Present -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-start animate-in-up">
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3 flex flex-col">
              <h3 class="heading-3 mb-2">
                03. <small class="block text-base font-normal opacity-75" style="font-size:50%"
                  >The Present</small
                >
              </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9">
              <p>
                Today, I'm walking the path of <span class="font-bold">product design</span> — adding
                <span class="italic">strategy</span> and <span class="italic">UX thinking</span> to my
                toolkit, aiming to understand not just <span class="font-bold">how to build</span>,
                but <span class="font-bold">what to build</span> and <span class="font-bold"
                  >why</span
                >.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 04 - The Mission -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-start animate-in-up">
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3 flex flex-col">
              <h3 class="heading-3 mb-2">
                04. <small class="block text-base font-normal opacity-75" style="font-size:50%"
                  >The Mission</small
                >
              </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9">
              <p>
                I <span class="font-bold">create to solve</span>. For <span class="italic"
                  >clients</span
                >. For <span class="italic">users</span>. For the <span class="font-bold"
                  >products I believe in</span
                >. My focus is on <span class="font-bold"
                  >helping digital products grow with clarity</span
                > — and shaping the <span class="italic">tools I'd want to use myself</span>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 05 - The Learning -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-start animate-in-up">
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3 flex flex-col">
              <h3 class="heading-3 mb-2">
                05. <small class="block text-base font-normal opacity-75" style="font-size:50%"
                  >The Learning</small
                >
              </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9">
              <p>
                A developer's journey is <span class="font-bold">never done</span>. New tools, new
                mindsets, new challenges — I keep learning to stay <span class="italic">sharp</span
                >, <span class="italic">adaptable</span>, and <span class="italic"
                  >ready for what's next</span
                >.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 06 - The Vision -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-start animate-in-up">
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3 flex flex-col">
              <h3 class="heading-3 mb-2">
                06. <small class="block text-base font-normal opacity-75" style="font-size:50%"
                  >The Vision</small
                >
              </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9">
              <p>
                Beyond code and design, I believe in <span class="font-bold"
                  >building things that last</span
                > — <span class="italic">products with purpose</span>, <span class="italic"
                  >interfaces that matter</span
                >, and <span class="font-bold">ideas that evolve into something real</span>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 07 - The Future -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 items-start animate-in-up">
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-3 flex flex-col">
              <h3 class="heading-3 mb-2">
                07. <small class="block text-base font-normal opacity-75" style="font-size:50%"
                  >The Future</small
                >
              </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-9">
              <p>
                <span class="font-bold">Ideas become products.</span>
                <span class="italic">Side-projects become platforms.</span> I'm <span
                  class="font-bold">building tools to help others</span
                > — and to power <span class="italic">my own vision</span>.
              </p>
              <p class="mt-4 font-bold italic">
                Always curious. Always building. Always delivering.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-group about-descr__btnholder animate-in-up">
          <a
            class="btn btn-default hover-default"
            href="/pdf/_David_Verta_RESUME.pdf"
            target="_blank"
          >
            <em></em>
            <span class="btn-caption">Download CV</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-4 md:gap-8">
          <div class="md:col-span-8">
            <div class="divider divider-image about-image-1 animate-in-up"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="about-info__item animate-in-up">
              <h6>David Verta</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="about-info__item animate-in-up">
              <h6>
                <a class="link-inline text-link" href="tel:+5491112345678">+54 9 11 3574 5491</a>
              </h6>
            </div>
            <div class="about-info__item animate-in-up">
              <h6>
                <a class="link-inline text-link" href="mailto:me@deiv.dev">me@deiv.dev</a>
              </h6>
            </div>
            <div class="about-info__item animate-in-up">
              <h6>
                <a
                  class="link-inline text-link"
                  href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/xMJXTEUeHkv6kYRQ6"
                  target="_blank">Buenos Aires, Argentina</a
                >
              </h6>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="achievements d-flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-8">
          <div class="achievements__item d-flex flex-col grid-item animate-card-3">
            <div class="achievements__card">
              <p class="achievements__number animate-in-up">40+</p>
              <p class="achievements__descr animate-in-up">Happy clients</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="achievements__item d-flex flex-col grid-item animate-card-3">
            <div class="achievements__card">
              <p class="achievements__number animate-in-up">2+</p>
              <p class="achievements__descr animate-in-up">Years of experience</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="achievements__item d-flex flex-col grid-item animate-card-3">
            <div class="achievements__card">
              <p class="achievements__number animate-in-up">50+</p>
              <p class="achievements__descr animate-in-up">Projects done</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
